DROPPING UNWANTED COLUMNS¶

Let us drop instant bcoz it is just the index for each row,dteday bcoz it only shows date which can be observed with the help of yr and mnth columns,casual and registered column bcoz combination of these two shows cnt column

In [94]:
#dropping columns
day.drop(['instant','dteday','casual','registered'],axis = 1,inplace = True)
In [95]:

#Generic function to calculate VIF of variables

def calculateVIF(df):
    vif = pd.DataFrame()
    vif['Features'] = df.columns
    vif['VIF']=[variance_inflation_factor(df.values,i) for i in range(df.shape[1])]
    vif['VIF'] = round(vif['VIF'],2)
    vif = vif.sort_values(by = 'VIF',ascending=False)
    return vif
